PRICE IMPROVEMENT PLUS $10K IN BUYER INCENTIVES TOWARD CLOSING COSTS OR RATE BUYDOWN! ASSUMABLE VA LOAN WITH 3.25% INTEREST RATE! 

Welcome to this beautiful two story home with a pool in Pepper Hill! Conveniently located right outside of Gate 2 this spacious home has lots to offer. There are 5 bedrooms with the primary on the main floor, a large kitchen with island perfect for entertaining and boasting granite countertops. New flooring throughout the main level. Downstairs half bath recently refinished. There is a 3 car garage with two of the garage doors having been replaced with insulated doors. A large loft area upstairs with plenty of room for a second living room space or even a movie room. The remaining 4 bedrooms are upstairs as well with two full baths. Fall in love with the outdoor oasis in the backyard. The salt water pool was built by Pete Alewine 4 years ago. Gazebo with table and chairs to remain. This home is totally electric and energy efficient. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your new home!
